{"tid":2167353,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拜登斥特朗普帶來黑暗與分裂　自己可帶來希望與光明","createTime":"2020-08-21T05:12:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T11:42:36.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":78,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"19b6fe71dc914d821a5e3a479e7667aedd07cd5e","tid":2167353,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:12:34.000Z","msg":"美國民主黨最後一日全國代表大會，前副總統拜登正式接受總統候選人提名。<br />\n<br />\n他在特拉華州發表接受提名演說，形容特朗普政府為美國帶來黑暗、憤怒、仇恨、分裂，自己若當選會為美國帶來希望與光明，將不分黨派為美國民眾服務。<br />\n<br />\n拜登又指，美國是全球最多人確診新型肺炎的國家，批評特朗普不負責任、推諉過失，認為民眾不應該再給予特朗普掌權4年的機會。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1545048-20200821.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1545048-20200821.htm&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliu%2Fkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=a9ae989b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1545048-20200821.htm&h=398d8261\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1545048-20200821.htm</a>"},{"pid":"e6533b6c377750db106dcb079dc60f62b0295f92","tid":2167353,"uid":23061,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:14:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />creepy"},{"pid":"2fa699ebf22bac5b255a783a09b08b412a7dee38","tid":2167353,"uid":37528,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:15:28.000Z","msg":"妹妹，伯伯帶光明同希望俾你，跟伯伯黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92a47700c27d05c955d0bada14b3559bc4345f73","tid":2167353,"uid":67468,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:15:34.000Z","msg":"有病睇醫生"},{"pid":"5426006abb74486454d8d82ea6dadc8b04ee46e2","tid":2167353,"uid":127575,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:15:45.000Z","msg":"幼幼光明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.